Title: IFTTT Applet Execution Sequence

participant User
participant IFTTT as "IFTTT Platform"
participant Trigger as "Trigger Service"
participant Action as "Action Service"

User->IFTTT: Creates an applet
User->IFTTT: Defines the "if this" trigger
User->IFTTT: Defines the "then that" action

User->IFTTT: Specifies trigger settings
Trigger->IFTTT: Monitors the specified event

User->IFTTT: Specifies action settings
Action->IFTTT: Prepares to perform the action

Trigger->Action: Trigger event occurs

Action->Action: Executes the specified action

Action->IFTTT: Reports action completion
IFTTT->User: Notifies the user of applet execution
